{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1700-05_187","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"[Ode]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mai 1700 [tome 5], p. 187-192.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"L’Ode que vous allez lire est du Pere Dumoret, Prestre de la Doctrine Chrestienne, Professeur de Rethorique du College de Lesquille à Toulouse. C’est le même qui avoit composé l’Ode contre l’Heresie, qui concourut pour le prix avec l’Ode de la Poësie, aussi bien que celle-cy.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"CONTRE LES IMPIES.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel objet me frape &amp; m’enchante ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel feu m’emporte loin de moy ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Divinité que j’apperçoi,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Viens soûtenir ma voix tremblante.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Portez sur les ailes des vents","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Déja mes concerts éclatans","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Font retentir la terre &amp; l’onde.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Applaudissez, Peuples divers,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est le Dieu qui forma le monde","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que je vais chanter dans mes Vers.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Estre toûjours, c’est son partage.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout vit, tout se meut à sa voix.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Soumis aux forces de ses loix","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Flots respectent leur rivage.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Cieux il forma les ressorts ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Vents tirez de ses tresors","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le benissent par leur murmure :","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seul insensé blasphemateur","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Impie, horreur de la nature,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne connoist point son Createur.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fiéres merveilles qu’on admire,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Beautez, dont les charmes vainqueurs","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Séduisent tant de foibles cœurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et les rangent sous vostre empire !","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cet éclat dont vous vous flatez,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces traits, ces appas si vantez","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Viennent du Dieu qui vous fit naistre ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et l’homme, esclave de ses sens,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Renonce à cet Auguste Maistre,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vous prodigue son encens.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel bruit confus me vient surprendre ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quels cris font retentir les airs ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout parle dans cet Univers ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Enfer, les feux se font entendre.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pleins de justes ressentimens","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je voi le Ciel, les Elemens","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’armer de parole &amp; de vie.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seigneur, anime leur ardeur,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et fais desormais que l’Impie","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Te reconnoisse à ta grandeur.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que frappé d’une heureuse crainte","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il commence à porter ses yeux","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur ces Tableaux misterieux","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où ta Sagesse s’est dépeinte.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Visible source de la Foy,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour ramener son cœur à toy","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Univers deviendra son maistre,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et par tout tes rayons épars,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour le forcer à te connoistre,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Viendront s’offrir à ses regards.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de spectacles se presentent !","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de charmes victorieux !","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Astres qui brillez dans les Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que vos merveilles nous enchantent !","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Createur dans vos rayons","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A tracé les nobles crayons","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ses grands &amp; sacrez misteres ;","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et découvre avec majesté","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans vos visibles caracteres","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son invisible immensité.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une clarté vive &amp; feconde","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Soleil répand les attraits,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de mille tresors secrets","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enrichit l’un &amp; l’autre Monde.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Constant dans son cours lumineux","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du Jour, ouvrage de ses feux","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il ouvre &amp; ferme la barriere ;","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais cet Astre resplendissant","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fait moins admirer sa lumière","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que la splendeur du Tout-puissant.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les ans d’une égale vitesse","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Amenent les fleurs, les glaçons ;","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On voit les Mois &amp; les Saisons","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mourir &amp; renaistre sans cesse.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les siecles dans leurs changemens","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont tous les mêmes mouvemens,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et se montrent pour disparoistre :","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Nature par tant de traits","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’empresse à nous faire connoistre","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[9]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Dieu","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[9]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"qui ne change jamais.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[9]/hi[2]/#"}}]}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que tout celebre vos ouvrages ;","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’à vous benir tout soit constant,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Seigneur,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"dont le pouvoir s’étend","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/hi[1]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au-delà des temps &amp; des âges.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que renonçant à ses fureurs","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Impie admire les faveurs","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont vous sçavez combler nos ames ;","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que touché d’un bien si doux,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il ne brûle que de vos flâmes","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et ne soûpire que pour vous.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}}]}}}